==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Coulombs law
<hw>Cou`lomb's" law</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Physics)</fld> <def>The law
that the force exerted between two electric or magnetic charges is
directly proportional to the product of the charges and inversely to the
square of the distance between them.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coulter</ent>⟦br⟧
